Any advice?? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utheminimage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Mini Mage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#333333>(6/3/02 10:52:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=380.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: How the hell do I kite specs??</span><hr size=1> I cant say i know much about Kiting Specs, but what i use to tell when my pet had gained agro is to just open up theinventory thing (where u can see your character and equipment) and turn a little bit to the left/right while running so i can see when im no longer being followed<br>
