hange I've tried the wandering Ogre guards in zone or the Giants next door in RM.  I wish I started there sooner.<br>
<br>
The only downside is the occasional Spec add that seems to come out of nowhere, but I've only had to Gate to safety once.  The rest have been &quot;pleasent surprises&quot;.<br>
<br>
Come back when you're lvl 44 or 45.<br>
